rComments: She has good lectures, and an easy class. However, seems hell-bent on turning a science class into a social Science class. Nothing is ever clearly defined, and the material is barely connected to the science or protocols of forensic sciences.   Good professor, just has wrong grasp of the course. Would not take this professor for this course.
Best prof at utm, love the lectures, so nice and best looking prof ever. Definitely a role model.
